text: ( Source : Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia ) Jakarta , 16/10/ 2015 Kemenkeu - In the meeting with the Budgetary Board of DPR RI, the potential of budget deficit in RAPBN 2016 is set at 2.15 percent to Gross Domestic Product
